<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.4.5">
<l>māluṅ kaṭalā ramalaik kuvaṭiṭ ṭaṇaikaṭ ṭivaram puruva maticēr</l>
<l>kōla matiḷā yavilaṅ kaikeṭap paṭaitoṭ ṭorukā lamari lati</l>
<l>kāla mituveṉ ṟayaṉvā ḷiyiṉāl katirnīṇ muṭipat tumaṟut tamarum</l>
<l>nīla mukilvaṇ ṇaṉemak kiṟaivaṟ</l>
<l>kiṭammā malaiyā vatunīr malaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place for our god, the one the color of dark clouds who rested,</l>
<l rend="indent">having placed mountains and hillocks to fill the glorious sea,</l>
<l>Building a dam, when [he] penetrated the boundary to ruin Lanka,</l>
<l rend="indent">with ornate walls that reached the moon,</l>
<l>Having thought, ‘Now is the time,’ discharging a weapon once</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the battlefield reverberated,</l>
<l>Severing the ten glittering high crowns with the Aja-arrow,</l>
<l rend="indent">is the great mountain, namely Nīrmalai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
